Module chav1961.purelib

Package chav1961.purelib.basic.subscribable

This package contains a set of subscribable containers for all significant Java types. Every container keeps current value of the given type and a list of listeners associated with the given instance. When value in the container changes, every listeners fire events about it.

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
